description:
Recently I was able to go hands on with the New MSI Claw 8 Ai Plus and in this video I wanted to give you first impressions.
Powered by the Intel Lunar Lake Core Ultra 258V and backed by 32GB of LPDDR5X Ram.
The New Claw 8 Ai Plus has n 8” 120Hz VRR Screen and 80Wh Battery. So will it be worth Buying?

Learn more Here about the MSI Claw 8 Ai Plus: https://www.msi.com/Handheld/Claw-8-AI-Plus-A2VMX
